    <h1 class="my-2 pt-3">Budget and Mid-Range Boracay Hotels and Resorts</h1>
    <blockquote>
    <p class="lead text-secondary">"Prices are subject to change without notice"</p>
    <footer class="blockquote-footer">Michael Aquino, Tripsavvy</footer>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="row">
